quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,“Ndikulumbilira mzinda uwu (wa Makka)
  90,2,“Ndipo iwe udzatsikira mu mzindawu mwa ufulu (ndi kuuonjezera ulemelero)
  90,3,"“Ndiponso ndikulumbilira chobereka ndi choberekedwa, (kudzera mwa iwo mtundu wa anthu udasungidwa)"
  90,4,“Ndithudi tamulenga munthu mmavuto (kuyambira chiyambi chake mpaka malekezero a moyo wake)
  90,5,“Kodi (munthu wolengedwa ndi mavutoyu) akuganiza kuti palibe amene angamuthe
  90,6,"“Akunena (monyadira kuti): “Ndaononga chuma chambiri (chifukwa choletsa Chisilamu kufala).”"
  90,7,“Kodi akuganiza kuti palibe akumuona
  90,8,“Kodi sitidampangire maso awiri (amene akuyang’anira)
  90,9,“Ndilirime ndi milomo iwiri (zimene akulankhulira)
  90,10,"“Ndipo tamlongosolera njira ziwiri: (yabwino ndi yoipa, ndipo tampatsa mphamvu yosankhira njira imene akufuna)"
  90,11,“Kodi walikwera phiri lovutalo (lomwe lingakamfikitse ku Jannah)
  90,12,“Nanga nchiyani chakudziwitsa za kukwera phiri lovutalo
  90,13,“(Kutero ndiko) kupereka ufulu kwa kapolo
  90,14,“Kapena kuwadyetsa (osowa) pa tsiku la njala
  90,15,“Amasiye achibale
  90,16,“Kapena wosauka wa fumbi lokhalokha (chifukwa cha kuvutika kwambiri)
  90,17,"“Komanso nakhala mmodzi mwa okhulupirira ndikumalangizana za kupirira, ndi kumalangizananso za chifundo"
  90,18,“Otero ndiwo (anthu abwino) a ku dzanja lamanja
  90,19,"“Koma amene sanakhulupirire Ayah Zathu, ndi anthu a kudzanja lamanzere (oipa)"
  90,20,“Moto wozungulira mbali zonse udzakhala pa iwo (ndikuwatsekera makomo)
  91,1,“Ndikulumbilira dzuwa ndi dangalira lake
  91,2,“Ndi mwezi pamene ukulitsatira (dzuwalo ndikulowa mmalo mwake powalitsa dziko dzuwalo litalowa)
  91,3,“Ndi usana pamene ukulisonyeza poyera (kuti lisaphimbidwe)
  91,4,“Ndi usiku pamene ukuliphimba
  91,5,“Ndi thambo ndi (Mwini mphamvu zonse Wamkulu) Yemwe adalimanga ndi kulitukula (mwaluso)
  91,6,"“Ndi nthaka ndi (Mwini mphamvu zonse Wamkulu), Yemwe adaiyala (mbali zonse ndi kuichita kukhala ngati choyala)"
  91,7,“Ndi mzimu ndi Yemwe adawulinganiza (powupatsa mphamvu)
  91,8,“Ndipo adaudziwitsa zoipa zake ndi zabwino zake; (ndi kuwupatsa ufulu ndi mphamvu zochitira zimene ukufuna)
  91,9,“Ndithu wapambana amene wauyeretsa
  91,10,“Ndipo ndithu wataika amene wauononga
  91,11,“Thamud (Samudu) adakanira (Mneneri wawo) chifukwa cha kulumpha malire kwawo
  91,12,“Pamene woipitsitsa wawo adadzipereka (kupha ngamira yozizwitsa)
  91,13,"“Pamenepo Mneneri wa Allah (Swaleh) adawauza: “Isiyeni ngamira ya Allah (idye mdziko la Allah). Musailetse kumwa madzi (pa tsiku lake).”"
  91,14,“Koma adamutsutsa ndikuipha; kwa chifukwa chimenecho Mbuye wawo (Allah) adawaononga chifukwa cha tchimo lawo; adangowafafaniza (onse mnthaka)
  91,15,“Iye saopa zotsatira za chilangochi (chifukwa amenewa ndi malipiro a chilungamo pa zomwe adachita)
  92,1,“Ndikulumbilira usiku pamene ukuphimba (chilichonse)
  92,2,“Ndi usana pamene kukuyera
  92,3,“Ndiponso Yemwe adalenga chachimuna ndi chachikazi
  92,4,“Ndithu zochita zanu nzosiyanasiyana
  92,5,“Tsono yemwe akupereka (pa njira ya Allah) ndikumamuopa (Mbuye wake ndikupewa zoletsedwa)
  92,6,“Ndikumavomereza zinthu zabwino; (komwe kuli kukhulupirira Allah mwanzeru)
  92,7,“Choncho timufewetsera njira yompititsa ku zabwino
  92,8,“Koma uyo achite umbombo ndikuganiza za kuti iye payekha ngokwana
  92,9,“Ndi kumatsutsa zinthu zabwino
  92,10,“Choncho timufewetsera njira yompititsa ku mavuto (a muyaya)
  92,11,“Ndipo chuma chake sichidzamthandiza (chilichonse) akadzagwera ku Moto
  92,12,“Ndithu Ife ndi amene timawalongosolera anthu njira yabwino ndi njira yoipa
  92,13,“Ndipo ndithu moyo womaliza ndi moyo woyamba uli m’manja mwathu
  92,14,"“Basi, ndikukuchenjezani za Moto woyaka mwa mphamvu"
  92,15,“Sakaulowa koma (kafiri) woipitsitsa kwambiri
  92,16,“Yemwe amatsutsa (choona) ndi kunyoza (zisonyezo za Allah)
  92,17,“Koma yemwe akuopa Allah kwambiri akatalikitsidwa ndi Moto
  92,18,“Amene akupereka chuma chake ndi cholinga chodziyeretsa
  92,19,"“Ndipo palibe aliyense kwa iye, amene adamchitira za chifundo zomwe zikulipidwa"
  92,20,“Koma (akuchita zimenezi) kufuna chikondi cha Mbuye wake Wapamwambamwamba
  92,21,“Ndipo posachedwa adzasangalala
  93,1,“Ndikulumbilira mmawa dzuwa litakwera (imene ili nthawi yantchito)
  93,2,“Ndi usiku pamene ukuvindikira
  93,3,“Sadakusiye Mbuye wako (iwe Mneneri) (s.a.w) ndiponso sadakude
  93,4,“Ndithu moyo watsiku lirimkudza ndi wabwino kwa iwe kuposa umoyo woyambawu
  93,5,“Ndithu posachedwapa akupatsa Mbuye wako (zabwino zamdziko lapansi ndi tsiku lachimaliziro) ndipo ukondwera
  93,6,“Kodi sadakupeze uli wa masiye ndipo adakupatsa pokhala pabwino
  93,7,“Ndipo adakupeza uli wosazindikira (Qur’an) nakuongola (pokuzindikiritsa Qur’aniyo ndi malamulo a chipembedzo)
  93,8,“Ndiponso adakupeza uli wosauka nakulemeretsa
  93,9,"“Basi, wamasiye usamchitire nkhanza"
  93,10,“Ndiponso wopempha usamukalipire
  93,11,“Tsono mtendere wa Mbuye wako uwutchule (pothokoza ndi kugwira ntchito zabwino)